race.comment: DO SOMETHING (4) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (34.44) from Box 8 at Sandown over 595m. Has ability and can bounce back. PAW LOUIS (3) missed the frame last time when fourth (34.64) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Has a good record here including four wins. Shapes as one to consider. REALITY PIE (1) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and two minors from 12 tries. Was out of placings last time (29.95) at Sandown in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 9 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. DESIRABILITY (8) looks an each-way chance. Something for the Multiples: SMOOTH PRINCE (7)
